    public static enum IDManager.VertexIDType
extends Enum<IDManager.VertexIDType>
    bit mask- Description (+ indicates defined type, * indicates proper & defined type) 0 - + User created Vertex 000 - * Normal vertices 010 - * Partitioned vertices 100 - * Unmodifiable (e.g. TTL'ed) vertices 110 - + Reserved for additional vertex type 1 - + Hidden 11 - * Hidden (user created/triggered) Vertex [for later] 01 - + Schema related vertices 101 - + Schema Type vertices 0101 - + Relation Type vertices 00101 - + Property Key 000101 - * User Property Key 100101 - * System Property Key 10101 - + Edge Label 010101 - * User Edge Label 110101 - * System Edge Label 1101 - Other Type vertices 01101 - + Vertex Label 001 - Non-Type vertices 1001 - * Generic Schema Vertex 0001 - Reserved for future
